Package edu.ucla.wise.client

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppImageRenderServlet
    AppImageRenderServlet class is used to get an image form database and in-case it fails it tries to get it from file system.
    AppStyleRenderServlet
    AppStyleRenderServlet class is used to get an Style sheets from database.
    BeginServlet
    BeginServlet is a class which is used to direct the user coming from email URL or interviewers to appropriate next step or page.
    BrowserRequestChecker
    BrowserRequestChecker is used to check the User associated with the session.
    ConsentDeclineServlet
    ConsentDeclineServlet is a class used to record declining consent reason.
    ConsentGenerateServlet
    ConsentGenerateServlet is a class is used to generate the consent form.
    ConsentRecordServlet
    ConsentRecordServlet is a class which leads user to the survey if he accepted the consent or lead him to the page to ask for decline reason if he declined the consent.
    DeclineNOWServlet
    DeclineNOWServlet class is used if user declined the invitation from the email link, then forward him to the decline reason page.
    FreemarkerSurveyGenerateTest  
    IndexServlet
    TODO: This functionality is not possible in our current design because until we have study space ID we cannot decide which is the right study space the first page is related to.
    PrintStudySpaceServlet
    PrintStudySpaceServlet class used to print a study space, which should force a load.
    ProgressServlet
    ProgressServlet is a class used to display the sub menus to the left of the survey to review the completed pages of the survey.
    ReadFormServlet
    ReadFormServlet is used to update the results of the user taking the survey and redirecting them to a correct page based on the action.
    RepeatingItemHttpHandlerServlet
    RepeatingItemHttpHandlerServlet will handle deleting a repeating item from the database.
    RepeatingItemSetIOServlet
    RepeatingItemSetIOServlet will handle retrieving survey page values sent through AJAX calls currently implemented only for the repeating item set.
    RepeatingSetReadInputServlet
    RepeatingSetReadInputServlet will handle saving survey page values sent through AJAX calls currently implemented only for the repeating item set.
    SaveAnnoUserServlet
    SaveAnnoUserServlet is used to give anonymous users access to the survey.
    SaveAnnoUserTest
    TODO:This test is incomplete.
    SetupSurveyServlet
    SetupSurveyServlet sets up session for user to begin completing survey.
    SurveyorTestServlet
    SurveyorTestServlet initializes the surveyor application and displays some of the parameters.
    ThankYouGenerateServlet
    ThankYouGenerateServlet is used to handle the "Thank You" page.
    TriageServlet
    TriageServlet is used to direct the user after browser check to appropriate next step or page.
    UserHitCounter
    UserHitCounter class is used to keep track of number of users that are currently logged into the survey system.
    ViewFormServlet
    ViewFormServlet displays a single survey page as a form to be filled out.
    ViewOpenResultsServlet
    ViewOpenResultsServlet creates a summary report for each individual open question
    ViewResultsServlet
    ViewResultsServlet class is used to view the survey results (with the summary of data) by page (viewed by user through the Surveyor Application).
    WelcomeGenerateServlet
    WelcomeGenerateServlet generates the welcome page before displaying the consent form.
